 34  Link copied!\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Link copied!\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  After a two-week silence online,J.K.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1033, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0887357743012383e-44, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rowlingreturned to social media with more hatred directed atAlgerian boxer Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thenotoriously transphobicwriter resurfaced on X (formerly known as Twitter) after her rare social media silence.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0928059079222097e-39, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following her tweet on August 8, she posted for the first time on August 23 and wasted no time in reigniting controversy, targeting the Olympic gold medalist.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She returned to X to share an article by evolutionary biologist Colin Wright, who claimed thatImane's post-Olympics makeoveris nothing more than a \\\"hyper-feminizing PR campaign\\\" designed to distract people from the real issue: transparency about her gender.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.498432286972847e-13, \"text\": \"Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q42973\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_Lloyd_Wright\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:Mike Marsland/WireImage via Getty Images    Image credits:Jeux Olympiques / Imane Khelif via Instagram  The polarizing literary icon quoted one of the statements in Colin's article in her tweet: \\\"It's important to highlight that launching a PR campaign and applying layers of thick makeup requires far more time and effort than simply makingDNA test results public.\\\"\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 2045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marsland_Valley\", \"score\": 0.9999978732025617, \"rank\": 1.331339969271003e-06, \"text\": \"Marsland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marsland_Valley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marsland_Valley\"}, {\"begin\": 1693, \"end\": 1702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WireImage\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.336818289862348e-14, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of people in the comments section slammed the contentious public figure for her tweet.\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's important to highlight that launching a PR campaign and applying layers of thick makeup requires far more time and effort than simply making DNA test results public.\\\"\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- \\u270d\\ufe0f@SwipeWrighthttps://t.co/mRECJgNX3X  - J.K. Rowling (@jk_rowling)August 23, 2024    \\\"Born a woman.\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raised a woman.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Trained as a woman.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Competed as a woman over multiple years without issue,\\\" said one Imane supporter.\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You inventing a narrative and refusing to budge from it is why you have been so roundly mocked these last few weeks and why your lawyers will be very busy in the months to come.\\\"\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another comment said, \\\"I am not sure what you are achieving here Joanne.\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You made a mistake, and now you are insulting her.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The issue around gender equality is incredibly complex as you know, but perhaps your lawyers need to make this simpler for you.\\\"\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Beauty code (@beauty.code.officiel)    \\\"It was so nice when you were following legal advice to shut the f- up,\\\" read another comment, suggesting Rowling's two-week social media hiatus was likely due to her lawyers' recommendations afterImane filed a cyberbullying lawsuitagainst her.\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheHarry Potterauthor was one of the big names part of thecrusade against the 25-year boxer, apart fromElon Muskand Donald Trump.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3395, \"end\": 3407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8216200324130392e-13, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversy began during the 2024 Olympics, where Imane faced significant backlash after her victory overItalian boxer Angela Carini.\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3533, \"end\": 3546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103664941, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Almost immediately after the win, the Olympic gold winner faced allegations of being a man in a women's sport.\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea that those objecting to a male punching a female in the name of sport are objecting because they believe Khelif to be 'trans' is a joke.\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We object because we saw a male punching a female.https://t.co/KSAM5RCl1S  - J.K. Rowling (@jk_rowling)August 2, 2024    Could any picture sum up our new men's rights movement better?\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The smirk of a male who's knows he's protected by a misogynist sporting establishment enjoying the distress of a woman he's just punched in the head, and whose life's ambition he's just shattered.#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/Q5SbKiksXQ  - J.K. Rowling (@jk_rowling)August 1, 2024    Rowling had shared a picture from the Algerian boxer's match with Angela and accused her of being \\\"a man enjoying the distress of a woman he's just punched in the head.\\\"\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 4439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4308, \"end\": 4316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999902670352449, \"rank\": 7.894844497179757e-06, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She described her well-earned victory as a form of \\\"men reveling in their power over women.\\\"\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For all the emotional turmoil Imane went through, she is now seeking justice through a lawsuit filed with French authorities.\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4641, \"end\": 4647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999915580739791, \"rank\": 7.588506324425858e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has named Rowling and Elon in the cyber harassment lawsuit.\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Imane Khelif | \\u0625\\u064a\\u0645\\u0627\\u0646 \\u062e\\u0644\\u064a\\u0641 \\ud83c\\udde9\\ud83c\\uddff (@imane_khelif_10)    \\\"J. K. Rowling and Elon Musk are named in the lawsuit, among others,\\\" Nabil Boudi, her Paris-based attorney, toldVariety.\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4747, \"end\": 4759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 4819, \"end\": 4828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stars could face hefty fines and possibly even a prison sentence if the Olympic champion comes out victorious on the other side of the lawsuit.\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 5068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By entering your email and clicking Subscribe, you are agreeing to let us send you customized marketing messages about us and our advertising partners.\", \"from\": 5070, \"to\": 5221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are also agreeing to ourPrivacy Policy.\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you!\", \"from\": 5267, \"to\": 5277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have successfully subscribed to newsletters!\", \"from\": 5278, \"to\": 5326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone can write on Bored Panda.Start writing!\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Bored Panda onGoogle News!\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5385, \"end\": 5396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bored Panda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us onFlipboard.com/@boredpanda!\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"5  34  5  34  Link copied!\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Link copied!\", \"from\": 5481, \"to\": 5500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Writer,Entertainment News Writer  At Bored Panda, I dive into breaking celebrity news, Hollywood updates, and viral pop culture stories that spark global conversations.\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5598, \"end\": 5607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2494131580071726e-13, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My background as a reporter at International Business Times and Latin Times gave me experience covering fast-moving entertainment stories for international audiences.\", \"from\": 5678, \"to\": 5844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5711, \"end\": 5739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Business Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\"}, {\"begin\": 5744, \"end\": 5755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IBT_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Latin Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IBT_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IBT_Media\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, my work regularly appears on Google News, AOL, and MSN, reaching millions of readers.\", \"from\": 5845, \"to\": 5937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5883, \"end\": 5894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 5896, \"end\": 5899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AOL\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.722381452800887e-56, \"text\": \"AOL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AOL\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AOL\"}, {\"begin\": 5905, \"end\": 5908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MSN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999736247, \"rank\": 2.6511549781974898e-11, \"text\": \"MSN\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MSN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What excites me most is capturing the pop culture moments that people can not stop talking about.\", \"from\": 5938, \"to\": 6035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Writer,Entertainment News Writer  At Bored Panda, I dive into breaking celebrity news, Hollywood updates, and viral pop culture stories that spark global conversations.\", \"from\": 6037, \"to\": 6205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6126, \"end\": 6135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2494131580071726e-13, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My background as a reporter at International Business Times and Latin Times gave me experience covering fast-moving entertainment stories for international audiences.\", \"from\": 6206, \"to\": 6372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6239, \"end\": 6267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Business Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\"}, {\"begin\": 6272, \"end\": 6283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IBT_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Latin Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IBT_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IBT_Media\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, my work regularly appears on Google News, AOL, and MSN, reaching millions of readers.\", \"from\": 6373, \"to\": 6465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6411, \"end\": 6422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 6424, \"end\": 6427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AOL\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.722381452800887e-56, \"text\": \"AOL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AOL\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AOL\"}, {\"begin\": 6433, \"end\": 6436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MSN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999736247, \"rank\": 2.6511549781974898e-11, \"text\": \"MSN\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MSN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What excites me most is capturing the pop culture moments that people can not stop talking about.\", \"from\": 6466, \"to\": 6563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"JK.Rowling said one time she will happily be send in jail for being transphobic.\", \"from\": 6565, \"to\": 6645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would like her to fulfil that life-goal of her.\", \"from\": 6646, \"to\": 6695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no doubt as a cishet ally of the LGBTQ+ community that the homophobic Muslim country of Algeria had Imane tested through more credible means after the IBA's sham testing and if she *had* turned out to be trans, she'd have been executed as soon as they got those results, long before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 6697, \"to\": 7000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6765, \"end\": 6775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homophobia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9949983624598327e-24, \"text\": \"homophobic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homophobia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homophobia\"}, {\"begin\": 6776, \"end\": 6782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.5954884777184847, \"rank\": 0.6792936141770168, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}, {\"begin\": 6794, \"end\": 6801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999207293544, \"rank\": 7.924479375540087e-08, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 6857, \"end\": 6860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9995078077189139, \"rank\": 0.0004924346532128604, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because they are even more transphobic than J.K. Rowling is.\", \"from\": 7001, \"to\": 7061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7047, \"end\": 7051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0887357743012383e-44, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So what we have here is Rowling being so transphobic that she is bigoted against even cis women who dare to look even the tiniest bit masculine.\", \"from\": 7062, \"to\": 7206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be pathetic if she wasn't a billionaire, but her wealth makes her a dangerous threat to trans women and cis women alike.\", \"from\": 7207, \"to\": 7336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7306, \"end\": 7317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\", \"score\": 0.9700903339129996, \"rank\": 0.030831836007027283, \"text\": \"trans women\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane is male.\", \"from\": 7338, \"to\": 7352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I get this strange sense of schadenfreude whenever I think about JKR and Musk being named in Khelif's lawsuit... (BTW, Rowling only pretends to be a feminist, why would a feminist maintain connections with known abusers of women?\", \"from\": 7354, \"to\": 7583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's so fake.)\", \"from\": 7584, \"to\": 7599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure the sycophantic fans will come to defend their beloved billionaire and spew lies about Imane Khelif and other women, and display their anger at humans having rights.\", \"from\": 7600, \"to\": 7775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7699, \"end\": 7711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you know that anger is a secondary emotion?\", \"from\": 7776, \"to\": 7823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tell that to your neighborhood transphobe who insists they are not transphobic because \\\"phobia means fear and I am not afraid of trans people\\\".\", \"from\": 7824, \"to\": 7967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7914, \"end\": 7920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phobia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"phobia\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phobia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phobia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are afraid, and that makes them angry :)  I really hope that case has enough support to have both of those \\u00e0ssholes hauled into court.\", \"from\": 7968, \"to\": 8107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although in the real world, the best were likely to get is standing arrest warrants which effectively ban them from entering France.\", \"from\": 8108, \"to\": 8240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8235, \"end\": 8241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996463402731351, \"rank\": 0.00032181527794469475, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"JK.Rowling said one time she will happily be send in jail for being transphobic.\", \"from\": 8242, \"to\": 8322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would like her to fulfil that life-goal of her.\", \"from\": 8323, \"to\": 8372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no doubt as a cishet ally of the LGBTQ+ community that the homophobic Muslim country of Algeria had Imane tested through more credible means after the IBA's sham testing and if she *had* turned out to be trans, she'd have been executed as soon as they got those results, long before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 8374, \"to\": 8677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8442, \"end\": 8452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homophobia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9949983624598327e-24, \"text\": \"homophobic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homophobia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homophobia\"}, {\"begin\": 8453, \"end\": 8459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.5954884777184847, \"rank\": 0.6792936141770168, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}, {\"begin\": 8471, \"end\": 8478, \"title\": \"htt